    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--pill"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Selected work</span>
    <h1 style="font-size: var(--fs-3xl); margin-top: 1.2rem; max-width: 18ch;">Case studies, shipping soon.</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 46ch;">Competitor-Intel MCP, an automated product-generation pipeline, and an AI-ops workflow system — written up in full.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
